                    <head>Rawz̤at al-Ṣafāʼ by Mīr Khvānd, daftar 4-7 and epilogue</head>
                    <msContents>
                        <summary>Volumes (<foreign>daftar</foreign>) 4-7 and the epilogue
                                (<foreign>khāṭimah</foreign>), also known as the eighth volume of the
                                <title>Rawz̤at al-Ṣafāʼ</title>, a general history from the creation
                            of the world to the time of the author, by Muḥammad ibn Khāvandshāh
                            (1433–1498), known as Mīr Khvānd. Daftar 7 and the epilogue were
                            completed by his grandson, <persName role="aut" key="person_45109504"
                                >Khvānd Amīr</persName>. </summary>
                        <msItem xml:id="AIIT_Pers_1_01-item1">
                            <author key="person_175393012">
                                <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc">Muḥammad ibn Khāvandshāh Mīr
                                    Khvānd, 1433–1498 </persName>
                                <persName xml:lang="fa"/>
                            </author>
                            <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_273">Rawz̤at al-Ṣafāʼ</title>
                            <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_273">روضة الصفاء</title> <!--please make sure you include the key in all instances of encoded titles-->
        
                            <note>
                                <p>The colophons are dated between 1689 and 1691 but were not
                                    completed in chronological order, reflecting the fact that they
                                    were formerly separate fascicles, perhaps of multiple copies,
                                    which are now bound together. </p>
                                
                                <!--<p><locus from="1v" to="253v">ff. 1v-253v:
                                        </locus><title>daftar</title> 4. Colophon dated 5 Safar 1103
                                    (28 Oct 1691)</p> these are nested msItems! please follow the model below -->
                                <p><locus from="254v" to="445v">ff. 254v-445v:
                                        </locus><term>dafter</term> 5 Colophon dated 9 Rajab 1100
                                    (29 April 1689)</p>
                                <p><locus from="446v" to="766v">ff. 446v-766v:
                                        </locus><term>daftar</term> 6 Colophon 12 Zu 'l-Ḥijjah 1101
                                    (16 Sept 1690) at Thattah?</p>
                                <p><locus from="767v" to="890v">ff. 767v-890v:
                                        </locus><term>daftar</term> 7 Colophon dated 11 Jumādā I
                                    1101 (20 Feb 1690)</p>
                                <p><locus from="891v" to="930r">ff. 891v-930r:
                                        </locus><term>khātimah</term> Colophon dated 17 Muḥarram
                                    1102 (21 Oct 1690)</p>
                            </note>
                            <msItem xml:id="AIIT_Pers_1_01-item1-1"><locus from="1v" to="253v">ff. 1v-253v:
                            </locus><title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc">daftar 4</title> <note>Colophon dated 5 Safar 1103
                                (28 Oct 1691)</note></msItem>
    
                            <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                        </msItem>
                    </msContents>
